A [[exchange|currency_exchange]] offering trading for bitcoins against multiple euro.

Traders add funds through SEPA, iDEAL or other methods and then place normal or limit orders to buy and sell.

[[Bitcoin_Consultancy]] operates the exchange.

CleverCoin has a trading API.

##Trading
###Buying

A buy order is executed partially or in full when the price bid can be matched against a sell order that is at or below the bid amount.

###Selling

A sell order is executed partially or in full when the price asked can be matched against a buy order that is at or above the ask amount.

Fees are 0.3% for both buying and selling.

##Adding Funds
###BTC
Funds are available once [[confirmed|confirmation]] (3 confirms). No fees.

###EUR
The exchange accepts SEPA bank transfers for deposit.

##Withdrawing Funds

###BTC
For the withdrawal of bitcoins 0.0001 BTC is calculated (this is currently a standard netwerkfee of bitcoin).

###EUR
